    h4 API to execute readable regex
    label Enter a string to run an operation on
    br
    br
    input(id='inputString' type='text' placeholder='i.e. #1234' onkeyup='enableButton()')
    br
    label Select a simple operation to perform (all operations can be found on our docs page)
    br
    br
